text: The word superior means above or better. Superior may also refer to: ==Places== *Lake Superior, the largest of the North American Great Lakes, Canada, United States ===United States=== *Superior, Arizona *Superior, Colorado *Superior, Iowa *Superior, Montana *Superior, Nebraska *Superior, Wisconsin, a city *Superior (town), Wisconsin, a town adjacent to the city *Superior (village), Wisconsin, a village adjacent to the city *Superior, Wyoming ==Other uses== *Superior, a word used to describe positions in anatomy
